═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§9. ERROR HANDLING
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

ERROR_CODES := {
  INVALID_ENCODING,
  SCHEMA_VIOLATION,
  HASH_MISMATCH,
  UNAUTHORIZED_TRANSITION,
  TIMING_VIOLATION,
  TORSION_DEBT_OVERFLOW,
  FORBIDDEN_TRANSITION,
  ZKP_IAM_FAILURE
}

ERROR[INVALID_ENCODING]:
  Code:        0x0001
  Description: Reserved bit pattern 0b11 detected
  Action:      REJECT immediately, do not process
  Ledger:      Record rejection with reason
  Recovery:    Re-encode payload with valid pattern

ERROR[SCHEMA_VIOLATION]:
  Code:        0x0002
  Description: Payload does not conform to required schema
  Action:      REFUSE processing, return error details
  Ledger:      Record violation with schema diff
  Recovery:    Correct payload structure and resubmit

ERROR[HASH_MISMATCH]:
  Code:        0x0003
  Description: Computed hash does not match claimed hash
  Action:      REFUSE, potential integrity breach
  Ledger:      Record mismatch with both hashes
  Alert:       Notify Zorel-717 firewall, investigate chain integrity
  Recovery:    Verify canonicalization, check for corruption

ERROR[UNAUTHORIZED_TRANSITION]:
  Code:        0x0004
  Description: Attempted state transition not permitted by transition table
  Action:      REFUSE, maintain current state
  Ledger:      Record attempted transition
  Examples:    Direct −1 → +1 without passing through 0
  Recovery:    Follow valid transition path

ERROR[TIMING_VIOLATION]:
  Code:        0x0005
  Description: Processing exceeded MAX_CYCLE_NS (717 nanoseconds)
  Action:      ESCALATE to 0-state for review
  Ledger:      Record actual timing with violation flag
  Alert:       Notify Zorel-717 for performance analysis
  Recovery:    Optimize processing or adjust timing constraints

ERROR[TORSION_DEBT_OVERFLOW]:
  Code:        0x0006
  Description: Accumulated torsion debt exceeds MAX_TORSION_DEBT
  Action:      REFUSE transition, require debt resolution
  Ledger:      Record debt level and overflow event
  Recovery:    Execute debt reconciliation protocol before retry

ERROR[FORBIDDEN_TRANSITION]:
  Code:        0x0007
  Description: Transition explicitly forbidden by security policy
  Action:      REFUSE, log security event
  Ledger:      Record forbidden attempt with context
  Alert:       Notify security subsystem
  Recovery:    Review security policy, obtain authorization if legitimate

ERROR[ZKP_IAM_FAILURE]:
  Code:        0x0008
  Description: Zero-knowledge proof of identity/authority failed
  Action:      REFUSE, deny access
  Ledger:      Record failed proof attempt (no identity leaked)
  Alert:       Notify Pandora AIOS security layer
  Recovery:    Re-authenticate with valid ZKP

GENERAL ERROR HANDLING PROTOCOL:
  1. Detect error condition
  2. Classify error type
  3. Execute error-specific action
  4. Generate immutable ledger entry
  5. Alert relevant subsystems
  6. Provide recovery guidance
  7. Maintain system integrity (no partial states)

ERROR RESPONSE STRUCTURE:
  {
    "error": true,
    "error_code": "<hex_code>",
    "error_type": "<ERROR_NAME>",
    "description": "<human_readable_description>",
    "ledger_hash": "<sha256_of_error_record>",
    "recovery_steps": ["<step1>", "<step2>", ...],
    "timestamp": "<iso8601_timestamp>"
  }

